  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study aims to investigate the effect of a multi-disciplinary nutritional intervention
      program in geriatric nutritional at risk patients. The study is carried out as randomized
      controlled trial. The intervention consists of an individual dietary plan conducted by a
      clinical dietician before discharge in combination with three follow-up visits after
      discharge (1, 4 and 8 weeks).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
